Fr9CJr0fBbL3alBCvMSA">Sinh niên bất mãn bách - 生年不滿百</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-007/poem-uyvZo-PFSOVCpX-BvUVToA">Sơn cư bách vịnh kỳ 007 - 山居百詠其七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-T%C3%B4-t%E1%BB%A9-H%E1%BB%81/poem-bR8QGem88oZhdNps2IvS6Q">Tặng Tô tứ Hề - 贈蘇四徯</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/V%C5%A9-t%C3%ACnh-ch%C3%AD-giang-%C4%91%E1%BB%99/poem-pJqP-D3KRhyFJrEZ2UPLLg">Vũ tình chí giang độ - 雨晴至江渡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-cFCa0wn9ZwJZJ5nwtlsQmQ">Liễu Tông Nguyên</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
